<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10098371>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–17. Stenchaetothrips species. S. amamiensis sp. n., female 1–4: (1) Head & pronotum; (2) Antenna, right; (3) Metascutum; (4) Tergite VII. S. amamiensis sp. n., male 5–7: (5) Tergites VII–VIII, sculpture omitted; (6) Tergite IX, sculpture omitted; (7) Sternite VII, sculpture omitted. S. biformis, female 8–15: (8) Head & pronotum; (9) Postocular setae, setae I present; (10) Postocular setae, setae I absent; (11) Antenna, right; (12) Metascutum; (13) Tergite VII; (14) Posterior margin of tergite VII with large teeth; (15) Tergites VIII to X. S. biformis, male 16–17: (16) Tergite VII, sculpture omitted; (17) Sternite VII, sculpture omitted." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10098371/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10098377>
    dc:description "FIGURES 38–50. Stenchaetothrips species. S. pleioblasti sp. n., female 38–43: (38) Head & pronotum; (39) Antenna, right; (40) Mesonotum & metascutum; (41) Fore wing, right; (42) Tergite V & pleurotergite, right side; (43) Tergites VIII–X. S. pleioblastus sp. n., male 44–46: (44) Tergites VII–VIII, sculpture omitted at left side; (45) Posterior margin of tergite VIII with fine microtrichia; (46) Sternites VII–VIII, sculpture omitted. S. undatus. 47–50: (47) Head, female, from Fukushima Pref., Honshu; (48) Head, female, from Ishigaki-jima, Islands; (49) Antenna, female, from Ishigaki-jima Island; (50) Antenna, female, from Fukushima Pref., Honshu." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10098377/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10098373>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18–26. Stenchaetothrips species. S. dentatus sp. n., female 18–22: (18) Head & pronotum; (19) Antenna, right; (20) Tergite II, left side; (21) Tergite V, left side; (22) Tergite VIII, sculpture omitted at left side. S. langkawiensis, female 23– 26: (23) Head & pronotum; (24) Antenna, right; (25) Tergite VI, left side; (26) Tergites VIII–X." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10098373/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10098379>
    dc:description "FIGURES 51–61. Stenchaetothrips undatus 51–53: (51) Mesonotum & metascutum; (52) Tergite VII, left side; (53) Tergites VII–X, male, sculpture omitted at right side of tergites VII–VIII and tergite IX. Thrips alliorum, female 54–61: (54) Head & pronotum; (55) Antenna, right; (56) Metascutum; (57) Tergite VI & pleurotergite, left side; (58)Tergites VIII–X; (59) Sternite VII, sculpture omitted. T. alliorum, male 60–61; (60) Tergites IX–X; (61) Sternite VI." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10098379/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10098375>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27–37. Stenchaetothrips species. S. minutus, female 27–31: (27) Head & pronotum; (28) Antenna, right; (29) Metascutum; (30) Tergite VI, left side; (31) Tergites VIII–X. S. mucunae, holotype female 32–35: (32) Head & pronotum, sculpture omitted; (33) Antennal segments II–VII, left, microtrichia, setae and sensoria omitted; (34) Metascutum; (35) Tergite V, left side, sculpture omitted. S. mucunae, “allotype” male 36–37: (36) Tergite VI, left side, sculpture omitted; (37) Sternite VII, sculpture omitted." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10098375/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

